overview: Chinni Chinni Asalu Nalo Regene is a Telugu movie starring Keerthi Manu and Sonia Deepti in prominent roles. The cast also includes Pavan. It is a drama directed by Santhosh Nelanti with Rap Rock Shakeel as the Music composer and S.B. Uddhav as the editor forming part of the crew.
title: Chinni Chinni Asalu Nalo Regene
